Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located on the California coast!

Name: San Diego Natural History Museum
Description: The natural history museum in San Diego, California. A wonderful museum with fascinating exhibits, and my former workplace.

Name: Cat Therapy
Description: A cat café in downtown Santa Barbara with many cute cats.

Name: Crater Rock Museum
Description: A geological museum in Central Point, Oregon. It has a lot of interesting fossils and rocks.

Description: Another natural history museum-- as a paleontology student I'm fond of these. I used to go here as a kid!

Name: Maggie's Café
Description: A diner in San Diego, great pulled pork sandwiches and friendly waiters.
